\subtree{
\title{Key Insight: GF(3) = Naturality}
\p{\strong{GF(3) conservation IS the naturality condition} of Cat# equipment:}

\pre{\startverb
For a triad (s₋₁, s₀, s₊₁):
  Ran_K(s₋₁) →[bicomodule]→ s₀ →[bicomodule]→ Lan_K(s₊₁)
  
  The commuting square:
    G(f) ∘ η_A = η_B ∘ F(f)
    
  Becomes the GF(3) equation:
    (-1) + (0) + (+1) ≡ 0 (mod 3)
\stopverb}
}
}

